PrecisORDER RESPECTING THE WITHDRAWAL FROM DISPOSAL OF CERTAIN LANDS IN THE YUKON TERRITORY (Lhutsaw Wetland Habitat Protection Area, Y.T.) - which provides for the withdrawal from disposal of approximately 447.3 hectares in the Von Wilczek Lakes Area in order to facilitate the establishment of the LHUTSAW WETLAND HABITAT PROTECTION AREA, on behalf of the Selkirk First Nation.
